    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a high gloss, though close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front end and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It offers a smooth ride and solid mechanical performance, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
