    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in absolute showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior retains its original deep luster, complemented by an interior that shows zero signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been rigorously verified to meet factory specifications, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an unblemished specimen for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's absolutely stunning and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and honestly, it\u2019s in flawless shape inside and out. It drives like a total dream and has been babied since day one. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a flawless mechanical pedigree: the high-pressure double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearing service is documented. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive rear subframe reinforcement already performed. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The exterior maintains factory paint depth with zero oxidation, while the suspension kinematics remain sharp via fresh bushings and OEM-spec dampers. A turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Low mileage. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to acquire a truly museum-quality vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the showroom floor. Meticulously maintained by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a flawless finish with a deep, mirror-like gloss and a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Step inside to a cabin that remains in pristine condition, where the premium leather upholstery retains its original matte texture and suppleness without a single crease or sign of bolster wear. The interior still carries that unmistakable new-car scent, and every piece of technology and switchgear operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous 'open-checkbook' maintenance history with all services performed exclusively by authorized technicians. The undercarriage is equally clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. This vehicle comes complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service records. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this example stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in concours-level condition. Meticulously maintained and showing no discernible wear, it represents the pinnacle of its class. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin appointments, reflects an uncompromising standard of care. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this investment-grade vehicle is prepared for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to be parting with this beauty. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve babied it since the moment I got it. It\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's been cared for with a ton of love, you've found it. Come see it for yourself, I promise you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
