    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains mechanically flawless, featuring a meticulously maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies that deliver razor-sharp throttle response. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally perfect, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that retains its original rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior and interior show no signs of fatigue, making this a definitive collector\u2019s piece for the purist driver.",
